      <title>铃木预计到 2047 年印度汽车市场将增长五倍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/suzuki-sees-india-s-automobile-market-growing-fivefold-by-2047</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铃木汽车公司执行副总裁鲇川健一表示，得益于电动汽车的良好增长前景，印度汽车市场有望到 2047 年达到 2000 万辆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/suzuki-sees-india-s-automobile-market-growing-fivefold-by-2047</guid>
